longBusinessSummary: Getty Realty Corp. is a publicly traded, net lease REIT specializing in the acquisition, financing and development of convenience, automotive and other single tenant retail real estate. As of June 30, 2023, the Company's portfolio included 1,053 freestanding properties located in 39 states across the United States and Washington, D.C.
